{"tid":1988511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你支持攔炒 點解仲要戴口罩","createTime":"2020-04-25T09:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T10:46:39.000Z","uid":4672,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2e1bd0d15b5af61e67ddf22b283f87db2be8691e","tid":1988511,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:03:53.000Z","msg":"邊個會鍾意戴口罩 <br />\n<br />\n戴口罩核心意義係構成群體防禦<br />\n唔係保護你自己<br />\n<br />\n群體防禦係用黎保護老弱病幼<br />\n年輕人同青壯年根本唔會死於武肺（有長期病除外）<br />\n<br />\n隻病毒係專打老人家同長期病患<br />\n對年青人殺傷力同普通流感差唔多<br />\n<br />\n如果你支持攬炒 支持毒死曬廢中廢老<br />\n點解你要戴口罩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e3a5ab8c6213c7a106f023bf773174033941cb","tid":1988511,"uid":8833,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"犬隻發現 果然拉黑"},{"pid":"56fecb303b3ca7cb316212b5dfb3517d4e645b36","tid":1988511,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57e3a5ab8c6213c7a106f023bf773174033941cb","tid":1988511,"uid":8833,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"犬隻發現 果然拉黑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:05:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">果斷</span></span>"},{"pid":"f604ae6e10dff4b3b5941da65bb5949a224c4561","tid":1988511,"uid":4672,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57e3a5ab8c6213c7a106f023bf773174033941cb","tid":1988511,"uid":8833,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:05:09.000Z","msg":"犬隻發現 果然拉黑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:06:11.000Z","msg":"抗爭戴口罩 可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日常行街外出戴口罩 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7f321bf1bbea707882a8e12acedb9d8bba6e79","tid":1988511,"uid":194326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"57e3a5ab8c6213c7a106f023bf773174033941cb","tid":1988511,"uid":8833,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"cited